{"prompt": "Build a captivating website for a gourmet food delivery service. The design should prominently display a rich crimson.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Gourmet Delights</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f8f8f8;\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #800020; /* Rich Crimson */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 30px auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\n        }\n        .hero {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            position: relative;\n            background: linear-gradient(rgba(128, 0, 32, 0.7), rgba(128, 0, 32, 0.7)), url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x500/800020/ffffff?text=Delicious+Food') no-repeat center center/cover;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 100px 20px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: inset 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n        .hero h2 {\n            margin: 0 0 15px 0;\n            font-size: 2.8em;\n            letter-spacing: 1px;\n        }\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n        .menu-section {\n            margin-top: 40px;\n        }\n        .menu-section h3 {\n            text-align: center;\n            font-size: 2em;\n            color: #800020; /* Rich Crimson */\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            position: relative;\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n        .menu-section h3::after {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            bottom: 0;\n            left: 50%;\n            transform: translateX(-50%);\n            width: 80px;\n            height: 3px;\n            background-color: #800020; /* Rich Crimson */\n        }\n        .menu-items {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 25px;\n        }\n        .menu-item {\n            background-color: #fcfcfc;\n            border: 1px solid #eee;\n            border-radius: 6px;\n            padding: 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .menu-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        .menu-item img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n        .menu-item h4 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 1.4em;\n            color: #500010;\n        }\n        .menu-item p {\n            font-size: 0.95em;\n            color: #555;\n        }\n        .menu-item .price {\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: #800020; /* Rich Crimson */\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            margin-top: 10px;\n            display: block;\n        }\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: #800020; /* Rich Crimson */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            border: none;\n            cursor: pointer;\n        }\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #500010; /* Darker Crimson */\n            transform: translateY(-2px);\n        }\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            margin-top: 50px;\n            background-color: #333;\n            color: #eee;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n        footer a {\n            color: #800020; /* Rich Crimson */\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n        footer a:hover {\n            text-decoration: underline;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>Gourmet Delights</h1>\n    </header>\n\n    <section class=\"hero\">\n        <h2>Experience Culinary Excellence, Delivered.</h2>\n        <p>Savor exquisite dishes crafted with the finest ingredients, right at your doorstep.</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section class=\"menu-section\">\n            <h3>Our Signature Dishes</h3>\n            <div class=\"menu-items\">\n                <div class=\"menu-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/800020/ffffff?text=Truffle+Pasta\" alt=\"Truffle Pasta\">\n                    <h4>Truffle Tagliatelle</h4>\n                    <p>Handmade tagliatelle tossed in a creamy truffle sauce with fresh parmesan.</p>\n                    <span class=\"price\">$28.00</span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"menu-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/800020/ffffff?text=Seared+Scallops\" alt=\"Seared Scallops\">\n                    <h4>Pan-Seared Scallops</h4>\n                    <p>Jumbo scallops with a lemon-butter glaze, served with asparagus.</p>\n                    <span class=\"price\">$32.00</span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"menu-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/800020/ffffff?text=Ribeye+Steak\" alt=\"Ribeye Steak\">\n                    <h4>Prime Ribeye Steak</h4>\n                    <p>28-day dry-aged ribeye, grilled to perfection, with roasted garlic potatoes.</p>\n                    <span class=\"price\">$45.00</span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"menu-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/800020/ffffff?text=Chocolate+Lava\" alt=\"Chocolate Lava Cake\">\n                    <h4>Molten Chocolate Lava Cake</h4>\n                    <p>Rich dark chocolate cake with a warm, gooey center, served with raspberry coulis.</p>\n                    <span class=\"price\">$15.00</span>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 40px;\">\n                <button class=\"cta-button\">View Full Menu</button>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"menu-section\">\n            <h3>Why Choose Us?</h3>\n            <p style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 1.1em; max-width: 800px; margin: 20px auto;\">\n                At Gourmet Delights, we are passionate about food. We partner with local farms and artisan producers to source the freshest, highest-quality ingredients. Our chefs meticulously craft each dish, ensuring a memorable dining experience that you can enjoy in the comfort of your own home. Fast, reliable delivery and exceptional taste are our promises.\n            </p>\n             <div style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 40px;\">\n                <button class=\"cta-button\">Order Now</button>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Gourmet Delights. All rights reserved.</p>\n        <p>Contact us: <a href=\"mailto:info@gourmetdelights.com\">info@gourmetdelights.com</a></p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}